author_ssm: Jenny Gotwals, 2003; database migrated to Archivist Toolkit by Jennifer Gargiulo, 2016
unittitle_ssm: Robert L. Bracklow photograph collection
abstract_ssm:
Bracklow photographed New York City and surrounding areas around the turn of the century. He focused on architectural views, as well as areas or buildings that were being torn down to reshape the city environment. 
 
Glass negatives from Series I are digitized and available in the Shelby White and Leon Levy Digital Library.
corpname_ssm: Society of Amateur Photographers of New York
geogname_ssm: Harper's Ferry (W. Va.) -- Description and travel.
Staten Island (New York, N.Y.) -- Description and travel.
